fields.description: This is the that site you're currently on! This site is nothing complex but is my first app written that can be pulled and used as a template.
This is one of my first attempts at Django. This project is an attempt at cloning of Reddit. Utilizes authentication and validation for subreddit permissions.
Started as a simple blog but has been expanded to be a social networking blog. This project is constantly ongoing and what I expand on when I work on personal projects.
